citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"越碌個fb越覺得啲人恐怖<br />\n講埋晒啲矯情野咩人唔到最後唔行呢一步<br />\n但行到最後一步都要用最影響人既方式去做，睇唔到有太大值得同情既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9b30777803d5661bcb33680dc297d1a14f7ca1","tid":857244,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42cd0abe76890a46bb8ec9675f8ad806d63aba21","tid":857244,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"越碌個fb越覺得啲人恐怖<br />\n講埋晒啲矯情野咩人唔到最後唔行呢一步<br />\n但行到最後一步都要用最影響人既方式去做，睇唔到有太大值得同情既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"叫班撚屌一人夾錢起個碑係粉嶺站紀念個跳軌阻撚住哂大家搭車但又激起人反思新自由主義對人類生活模式影響的哲學英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa70bbd603bcf12bf4530facb2e5f36787ea1a86","tid":857244,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"fb入面啲人話人地要揀到自殺呢一步仲點會諗其他人 已經好可憐唔該諗下死者<br />\n屌咪說穿左佢到死都係自私，人地張圖講兩句心聲都起晒鋼，一味渣住死者為大呢樣野去judge人，咁點解唔去哀悼啲比美國同聯軍炸死既恐怖分子？炸到碎撚晒添呀死者為大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d293fbf12efd84cdb4aa09e9e4ea18b3ed29142f","tid":857244,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"如果一個人死左就一定無錯要企喺佢果邊幫佢，咁毛澤東希特拉仲有拉登都係聖人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4142d301a7c5169af778611d728145ed7c4ec9cc","tid":857244,"uid":150912,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"邊個廢柴係咁負皮呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放心啦你跳軌死我一樣會出post屌柒你件人間垃圾<br />\n唔好以為我會可憐你"},{"pid":"a7ba770147d0e5c4ce9f9af88225510374a16a63","tid":857244,"uid":22364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"嘩diu fb d大愛左膠屌撚到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a21826ef626e6a40daaaa4a8968cdc9c9a2d58e","tid":857244,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"住北區係低賤D"},{"pid":"78664f49b5881cc0fa7f25aafbe17956005bb9dd","tid":857244,"uid":41157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"佢有講錯咩？<br />\n<br />\n最撚仆街就係果啲冇受事件影響嘅塘邊鶴係度講風涼話"},{"pid":"581b1b871f0e375ffb129d7c5bd0ec27f8563953","tid":857244,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"盲幫跳軌死既人係咪痴線<br />\n仲要轉移視線問返工有無真係咁重要，但重點係佢係用呢個方式癱瘓晒所有搭呢條線既人既生活<br />\n唔單止返工既人，有可能係想睇仔女參加比賽既父母，有可能係趕去醫院見父母最後一面既仔女，佢地都會因為咁而有遺憾<br />\n講唔過人就去話人可以搭巴士，巴士都有limit 本來就係因為有火車先至令巴士既limit夠用，咁樣一跳唔止影響火車乘客，連巴士同其他公共交通都受影響 唔通死左就係大晒就係一定啱？大愛同左膠都唔係咁樣做架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1be2df42be399d262362fb3f031af5ae0129e7f","tid":857244,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ff6fdc76c72d84a1d646eb5482300be71d4d4b","tid":857244,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/114208_15410f57131bc48585c4eb05c96048bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice